invalid type: string "\u{f0b7}\nSpark Ignitor Inspection:\no Remove both spark igniters.\no Inspect the cable for damage\no Visually inspect and replace if any of the following are present:\n\u{f0a7}\ncenter electrode is eroded >0.63in.\n\u{f0a7}\nradial cracks or pieces are missing from the ceramic\n\u{f0a7}\ninsulator is broken, cracked, or loose on the terminal end.", expected f64and damage.\nn